channel.desc: Action 2021 As a bank teller, Guy discovers that his ordinary life is actually part of a famous video game. He embarks on a journey of exploration to find his true identity, encountering many strange and exciting characters along the way. Ryan Reynolds, Jodie Comer, Taika Waititi, Lil Rel Howery, Joe Keery, Shawn Levy, Matt Lieberman, Zak Penn.
